Okay, for those who DIDNT read the description: It is not online, it is LAN only. You can play with bots or friends at LAN, but you CANNOT (no, seriously) play online with this one. Only way to play CS online is to buy it.

As a matter of fact, If it is a LAN version you CAN PLAY ONLINE, but you will need a LAN-emulator, like Hamachi.

I have not tested it yet, though.
